he took my hand clean off and he swallowed it whole.

00:47:11.960 --> 00:47:13.830
是的，他肯定已经把这个消息传开了，
Yeah, he must have spread the word around,

00:47:13.960 --> 00:47:17.170
因为不到一个月，另一个人就夺走了我的腿
'cause within a month, another one had taken my leg.

00:47:17.310 --> 00:47:18.590
可能是 Skrill
Probably a Skrill.

00:47:18.730 --> 00:47:21.420
锯齿状牙齿，颌骨强度17
Serrated teeth, jaw strength 17.

00:47:21.560 --> 00:47:23.840
我要为你掉落的肢体报仇，大个子
I'll avenge your fallen limbs, big guy.

00:47:23.970 --> 00:47:25.390
我要砍掉你的手和脚
I'll chop off the hands and feet

00:47:25.530 --> 00:47:27.910
——我所见到的每一条龙 ——不
-of every dragon that I see. -Nah.

00:47:29.700 --> 00:47:31.460
你想要的是翅膀和尾巴
It's the wings and the tail you want.

00:47:31.600 --> 00:47:34.430
如果它们不能飞，它们就无法逃脱
If they can't fly, they can't get away.

00:47:34.570 --> 00:47:37.230
倒下的龙就是死龙
A downed dragon is a dead dragon.

00:47:37.370 --> 00:47:40.200
任何人都可以不依赖其他部分而生存下去
Anyone can get by without the other bits.

00:47:40.340 --> 00:47:41.940
我将失去我的所有肢体
I'm gonna lose all of my limbs.

00:47:42.030 --> 00:47:44.820
我自愿让拉夫纳特失去至少一条肢体
I volunteer Ruffnut to lose at least one limb.

00:47:44.960 --> 00:47:45.890
咦？
Huh?

00:47:46.030 --> 00:47:47.410
什么？
What?

00:47:47.550 --> 00:47:48.640
我们是双胞胎 你的痛苦就是我的痛苦
We're twins. Your pain is my pain.

00:47:48.720 --> 00:47:50.210
你们是双胞胎吗？
You're twins?

00:47:50.350 --> 00:47:52.380
甚至连我们的母亲都无法区分我们
Even our own mother can't tell us apart.

00:47:52.520 --> 00:47:54.420
这太不可思议了
It's uncanny.

00:47:54.560 --> 00:47:55.700
好了
There we go.

00:47:55.830 --> 00:47:57.730
阿斯特丽德的想法是正确的
Astrid's got the right idea.

00:47:57.870 --> 00:47:59.940
尽可能睡个好觉
Get your sleep while you can.

00:48:00.800 --> 00:48:02.460
很快，斯托伊克就会回来
Soon, Stoick will be back.

00:48:02.600 --> 00:48:05.360
你们之中的一个人将被选中去杀死那条龙
And one of you will be chosen to kill the dragon.

00:48:05.500 --> 00:48:08.500
WHO？
Who?

00:48:49.230 --> 00:48:50.510
无牙！
Toothless!

00:48:52.170 --> 00:48:53.620
早餐来啦
Brought breakfast.

00:49:00.280 --> 00:49:03.350
嗯？哥们，你觉得怎么样？
Huh? What do you think, bud?

00:49:03.490 --> 00:49:04.970
好的
Okay.

00:49:06.210 --> 00:49:08.660
我搞到了一些鳕鱼……
We got some cod...

00:49:09.530 --> 00:49:11.080
...一些鲑鱼
...some salmon

00:49:11.220 --> 00:49:13.010
还有一整条熏鳗鱼
and a whole smoked eel.

00:49:13.150 --> 00:49:15.740
哇啊啊啊啊啊……
Whoa, uh, uh, uh...

00:49:15.880 --> 00:49:17.850
没有鳗鱼！不抓鳗鱼！
No eel! Scratch the eel!

00:49:19.990 --> 00:49:23.330
是的，呃，我也不能说我喜欢它
Yeah, I, uh, can't say I love it, either.

00:49:28.680 --> 00:49:29.790
就是这样
That's it.

00:49:29.930 --> 00:49:31.890
坚持做好事
Stick to the good stuff.

00:49:32.030 --> 00:49:36.380
我马上就回来，
I'll just be back here,

00:49:36.520 --> 00:49:38.970
做好我自己的事
minding my own business.

00:49:41.900 --> 00:49:43.420
好的
Okay.

00:50:02.170 --> 00:50:05.070
好的 好的
Okay. Okay.

00:50:08.660 --> 00:50:11.420
呼 好吧 还不错
Whew. Okay. Not bad.

00:50:11.560 --> 00:50:12.660
它应该能起到作用
It could work.

00:50:12.800 --> 00:50:14.390
如果……哇哦！好吧！
If it's... Whoa! Okay!

00:50:14.520 --> 00:50:17.010
无牙！不行！天哪！
Toothless, no! Oh, gods!

00:50:20.050 --> 00:50:21.050
无牙！
Toothless!

00:50:21.150 --> 00:50:21.980
噢，天哪！
Oh, gods!

00:50:32.850 --> 00:50:34.960
起作用了！
It's working!

00:50:35.100 --> 00:50:37.750
耶！呼！
Yeah! Whoo!

00:50:44.310 --> 00:50:47.380
耶！呼！
Yeah! Whoo!

00:50:47.520 --> 00:50:49.730
今天的主题是团队合作
Today is all about teamwork.

00:50:49.870 --> 00:50:54.080
如果你们齐心协力，你们也许就能生存下来
If you work together, you might just survive.

00:50:55.250 --> 00:50:59.400
你看，湿了的龙头是点不着火的
You see, a wet dragon head cannot light its fire.

00:50:59.530 --> 00:51:02.090
但 Hideous Zippleback 则更加棘手，
But a Hideous Zippleback is extra tricky,

00:51:02.230 --> 00:51:05.260
因为一个头吸入气体，另一个头点燃气体
'cause one head breathes gas and the other head lights it.

00:51:05.400 --> 00:51:08.890
你的工作就是知道哪个是哪个
Your job is to know which is which.

00:51:09.030 --> 00:51:10.130
祝你好运
Good luck.

00:51:13.410 --> 00:51:17.720
锋利的毒牙可注入毒液进行消化
Razor-sharp fangs that inject venom for predigestion.

00:51:17.860 --> 00:51:20.620
— 更喜欢保留它的受害者... — 嘘！
-Prefers to keep its victims... -Shh!

00:51:20.760 --> 00:51:22.250
...有意识的
...conscious.

00:51:22.380 --> 00:51:25.080
你知道，我很高兴我们能够成为合作伙伴
You know, I'm kind of glad we got partnered.

00:51:25.970 --> 00:51:28.630
我们女孩必须团结在一起
Us girls got to stick together.

00:51:28.770 --> 00:51:30.670
—直到我不得不带你出去 —嘘
-Until I have to take you out. -Shush.

00:51:30.810 --> 00:51:32.760
我想我已经基本赢得了阿斯特丽德的青睐
I think I've pretty much won Astrid over.

00:51:32.840 --> 00:51:34.360
我的意思是，她几乎都不敢看我一眼
I mean, she can barely even look at me.

00:51:34.500 --> 00:51:37.230
看来你找对人了
You came to the right man for advice.

00:51:37.370 --> 00:51:38.990
-我没有问... -如果有一件事
-I didn't ask... -If there's one thing

00:51:39.130 --> 00:51:41.440
维京女孩的大脑无法抗拒，这是......
the Viking girl brain can't resist, it's...

00:51:41.580 --> 00:51:43.010
当心！
Look out!

00:51:44.790 --> 00:51:47.130
—嘿！—是我们，天才
-Hey! -It's us, geniuses.

00:51:47.270 --> 00:51:48.350
闪电般的反应
Lightning reflexes.

00:51:48.480 --> 00:51:49.890
我看到丑陋的头颅，我就攻击
I see hideous heads, I strike.

00:51:50.030 --> 00:51:51.790
哎哟
Ow.

00:51:51.930 --> 00:51:53.240
哇哦
Whoa.

00:51:53.380 --> 00:51:55.000
呃，做一个丑陋的头，阿斯特丽德
Uh, make that one hideous head, Astrid.

00:51:59.320 --> 00:52:01.420
拯救你们自己！
Save yourselves!

00:52:02.180 --> 00:52:04.320
也以玩弄受害者而闻名
Also known to toy with its victims,

00:52:04.460 --> 00:52:06.120
把他们肢解成碎片
dismembering them limb from limb.

00:52:06.260 --> 00:52:08.710
你能停止这样做吗？
Will you please stop that?

00:52:10.810 --> 00:52:12.050
鱼腿！
Fishlegs!

