搞错了
Wrong head.

00:52:19.920 --> 00:52:21.480
快离开那里，希卡普！
Get out of there, Hiccup!

00:52:23.100 --> 00:52:24.650
哦，来吧
Oh, come on.

00:52:34.800 --> 00:52:37.010
是啊 后退！
Yeah. Back!

00:52:38.390 --> 00:52:41.080
快跑……呃呃
Run... Hiccup.

00:52:41.220 --> 00:52:43.430
别让我再告诉你！是的
Don't make me tell you again! Yeah.

00:52:43.570 --> 00:52:45.880
嗯，没错 回到你的笔里
Yeah, that's right. Back in your pen.

00:52:49.200 --> 00:52:51.400
现在，想一想你做了什么
Now, think about what you've done.

00:53:09.910 --> 00:53:12.530
那么，我们今天完成了吗？
So, are we done today?

00:53:12.670 --> 00:53:15.740
因为今天我还有一些事情需要做，呃……
J-Just because I have some things I need to, uh...

00:53:16.710 --> 00:53:19.160
是的，我要...明天去见你们
Yeah, I'm gonna... I'm gonna see you guys tomorrow.

00:53:26.890 --> 00:53:27.750
咦？
Huh?

00:53:29.550 --> 00:53:30.750
嘿
Hey.

00:53:30.890 --> 00:53:32.240
哦，来吧
Oh, come on.

00:53:32.380 --> 00:53:33.690
尝试一下吧
Just try it.

00:53:43.770 --> 00:53:45.600
哇哦！
Whoa!

00:53:45.730 --> 00:53:47.430
噢，我要死了！
Oh, I'm gonna die!

00:53:48.600 --> 00:53:50.430
哇哦，哇哦，不！
Whoa, whoa, no!

00:53:52.260 --> 00:53:53.290
不，求你了！
No, please!

00:53:53.430 --> 00:53:56.470
只需调整一下自己的角度
Just kind of angle yourself.

00:53:56.610 --> 00:53:58.680
哇哦！
Whoa!

00:54:02.030 --> 00:54:04.240
哇哦，哇哦，不！
Whoa, whoa, no!

00:54:06.270 --> 00:54:08.310
噢，来吧！
Oh, come on!

00:54:23.740 --> 00:54:25.430
—让开！—走开！
-Out of my way. -Move!

00:54:25.570 --> 00:54:27.020
动起来，动起来，动起来，动起来，动起来！
Move, move, move, move, move, move!

00:54:27.160 --> 00:54:29.040
小心点，进入它的盲点
Watch yourselves. Get in its blind spot.

00:54:29.120 --> 00:54:30.500
我拿到了！这是我的！
I got it! It's mine!

00:54:30.640 --> 00:54:32.130
不，别把它带过来！
No, don't bring it over here!

00:54:44.930 --> 00:54:46.970
呃，小家伙 他叫什么名字？
Uh, little guy. What is his name again?

00:54:47.110 --> 00:54:49.270
-我不记得了 -嘿，慢点
-I don't remember. -Hey. Slow down.

00:54:49.380 --> 00:54:51.180
—你是想让我们出丑吗？—不，不是
-Are you trying to show us up? -N-No.

00:54:51.320 --> 00:54:52.990
我从未见过有人能如此打败 Gronckle
I've never seen someone take down a Gronckle like that.

00:54:53.080 --> 00:54:54.820
我的意思是，我一直都这样做，但你是如何学会的呢？
I mean, I do it all the time, but how did you learn?

00:54:54.910 --> 00:54:56.980
学什么？具体是什么？
Learn what? What exactly was that?

00:54:57.120 --> 00:54:59.120
好的，明白了，我很乐意解释一下
Okay, see, I-I'd love to explain.

00:54:59.260 --> 00:55:01.710
只是，我把我的斧头留在了拳击场里
It's just, I left my axe back in-in the ring.

00:55:01.850 --> 00:55:03.500
谁是好孩子？谁是好孩子？
Who's a good boy? Who's a good boy?

00:55:03.640 --> 00:55:05.470
哇哦，好的
Whoa, okay.

00:55:05.610 --> 00:55:07.750
是啊，是啊？你痒吗？
Yeah, yeah? You itchy?

00:55:07.890 --> 00:55:09.340
是那个地方吗？
Is that the spot?

00:55:43.990 --> 00:55:45.650
呃呃
Hiccup.

00:55:49.030 --> 00:55:50.650
哟，他在那里
Yo, there he is.

00:55:50.790 --> 00:55:52.650
嘿，希卡普
Hey, Hiccup.

00:55:52.790 --> 00:55:54.380
-好的 -呃呃 WW-等一下
-Okay. -Hiccup. W-W-Wait.

00:55:54.520 --> 00:55:56.300
-我有一个合适的问题 -所以我在想......
-I have a proper question. -So I'm thinking that...

00:55:56.380 --> 00:55:58.540
所需要的只是你和我站在拳击场上
All it needs to be is you and me in the ring.

00:56:07.220 --> 00:56:09.080
可怕的恐怖！
A Terrible Terror!

00:56:16.780 --> 00:56:18.400
它和我的一样大...
It's like the size of my...

00:56:19.610 --> 00:56:20.890
把它拿下来！
Get it off!

00:56:21.030 --> 00:56:22.720
拿开！拿开！
Get it off! Get it off!

00:57:49.980 --> 00:57:51.640
哎哟
Ow.

00:58:06.410 --> 00:58:08.270
其他船只呢？
And the other ships?

00:58:20.350 --> 00:58:21.910
爸爸！
Dad!

00:58:22.050 --> 00:58:23.050
我来拿
I got it.

00:58:24.500 --> 00:58:25.600
我很想念你
I missed you.

00:58:25.740 --> 00:58:27.670
就像是，以一种超级男子气概
In, like, a super manly way.

00:58:27.810 --> 00:58:30.160
我有很多关于火焰试炼的事情要告诉你
I got so much to tell you about the Trial of Flame.

00:58:30.290 --> 00:58:32.610
基本上是...爸爸？
It's basically between... Dad?

00:58:33.850 --> 00:58:35.230
爸爸？
Dad?

00:58:36.440 --> 00:58:37.470
爸...
Da...

00:58:37.610 --> 00:58:39.370
好的，我回家等你
Okay, I'll see you at home.

00:58:39.510 --> 00:58:41.720
那么，没有巢穴吗？
So, no nest, then?

00:58:41.860 --> 00:58:44.270
差远了
Not even close.

00:58:44.410 --> 00:58:46.350
我希望你能取得更大的成功
I hope you had more success.

00:58:46.480 --> 00:58:47.900
好吧，如果成功的话，
Well, if by success,

00:58:48.040 --> 00:58:49.680
你的意思是你的育儿烦恼已经结束了，
you mean your parenting troubles are over,

00:58:49.760 --> 00:58:51.940
那么，嗯，是的
then, uh, yeah.

