机会
Aye.

00:58:59.670 --> 00:59:01.640
没有人会忽视这种麻烦
No one will miss that nuisance.

00:59:03.910 --> 00:59:06.260
希卡普...
Hiccup is...

00:59:06.400 --> 00:59:07.500
走出去了吗？
gone?

00:59:07.640 --> 00:59:09.090
是的
Yeah.

00:59:09.230 --> 00:59:11.370
是的，大多数下午都是这样，但谁能责怪他呢？
Yeah, most afternoons, but who can blame him?

00:59:11.510 --> 00:59:13.340
名人的生活可能会非常艰难
The life of a celebrity can be very rough.

00:59:13.480 --> 00:59:14.960
他几乎无法穿过村庄
He can barely walk through the village

00:59:15.060 --> 00:59:17.830
而不会被他的大批新粉丝包围
without being swarmed by his army of new fans.

00:59:19.450 --> 00:59:21.900
谁能想到他有这个……
Who would've thought he has this...

00:59:22.040 --> 00:59:24.630
和野兽相处的方式？
way with the beasts?

00:59:36.570 --> 00:59:37.950
好的，伙计
All right, bud.

00:59:38.090 --> 00:59:40.540
我们会慢慢来
We're gonna take this nice and slow.

00:59:42.230 --> 00:59:43.710
开始了
Here we go.

00:59:43.850 --> 00:59:44.920
位置三
Position three.

00:59:45.060 --> 00:59:46.790
呃，不，四个
Uh, no, four.

01:00:02.630 --> 01:00:04.250
你准备好了吗？
You ready?

01:00:18.750 --> 01:00:20.610
来吧，来吧
Come on. Come on.

01:00:36.460 --> 01:00:38.530
是啊，看看我们！
Yeah, look at us!

01:00:38.660 --> 01:00:40.980
哇哦！
Whoa!

01:00:41.810 --> 01:00:44.290
我的错 我的错
My fault. My fault.

01:00:44.430 --> 01:00:46.260
是的，是的，我正在做
Yeah, yeah, I'm on it.

01:00:46.400 --> 01:00:47.710
位置五
Position five.

01:00:50.880 --> 01:00:52.330
来吧，伙计
Come on, bud.

01:00:56.650 --> 01:00:59.000
是啊 加油，宝贝！
Yeah. Go, baby!

01:00:59.130 --> 01:01:01.000
噢，这太神奇了！
Oh, this is amazing!

01:01:01.140 --> 01:01:02.960
我心中的风...
The wind in my...

01:01:03.100 --> 01:01:05.620
图纸！停！
Cheat sheet! Stop!

01:01:09.870 --> 01:01:12.560
噢，天哪！
Oh, gods!

01:02:20.900 --> 01:02:21.970
是的！
Yeah!

01:02:34.060 --> 01:02:34.990
儿子！
Son!

01:02:35.130 --> 01:02:36.680
爸爸！呃，你回来了
Dad! Uh, you're back.

01:02:36.820 --> 01:02:38.920
呃，呃，哦...好吧，呃，Gobber 不在这里，
Uh, uh, oh... Okay, uh, Gobber's not here,

01:02:39.060 --> 01:02:41.060
—所以，嗯...—我知道
-so, um... -I know.

01:02:43.480 --> 01:02:44.960
来找你了
Came looking for you.

01:02:45.100 --> 01:02:47.480
你你你做了什么？呃，为什么？
You-you-you did? Uh, wh-why?

01:02:47.620 --> 01:02:49.480
你一直在保守秘密
You've been keeping secrets.

01:02:49.620 --> 01:02:51.310
我有？
I have?

01:02:51.450 --> 01:02:54.280
你以为你能瞒我多久？
Just how long did you think you could hide it from me?

01:02:55.040 --> 01:02:56.800
我甚至不知道你在说什么……
I-I don't even know what you're talking...

01:02:56.940 --> 01:03:02.640
这个岛上发生的任何事我都听说过
Nothing happens on this island without me hearing about it.

01:03:03.910 --> 01:03:09.230
那么，我们来谈谈那条龙
So, let's talk about that dragon.

01:03:09.370 --> 01:03:10.780
噢，天哪，爸爸
Oh, gods, Dad.

01:03:10.920 --> 01:03:12.680
我-我-我真的很抱歉
I'm-I'm-I'm so sorry.

01:03:12.820 --> 01:03:14.200
我早就该告诉你了
I-I was gonna tell you sooner.

01:03:14.340 --> 01:03:15.960
— 我—只是不知道……
- I - just didn't know...

01:03:21.480 --> 01:03:23.730
你不生气吗？
You're not upset?

01:03:23.860 --> 01:03:25.900
啥？啥？
What? What?

01:03:26.040 --> 01:03:28.040
我本来希望如此
I was hoping for this.

01:03:28.180 --> 01:03:29.870
— 是吗？— 哦，是的
-You were? -Oh, yes.

01:03:30.010 --> 01:03:33.050
相信我，情况只会变得更好
And believe me, it only gets better.

01:03:33.180 --> 01:03:35.220
等你溢出来
Just wait till you spill

01:03:35.360 --> 01:03:37.360
第一次感受到纳德的胆量
a Nadder's guts for the first time.

01:03:37.500 --> 01:03:42.470
或者，或者将你的第一个 Gronckle 头颅安装在长矛上
Or-or mount your first Gronckle head on a spear.

01:03:42.610 --> 01:03:44.510
多么奇妙的感觉啊
What a feeling.

01:03:44.640 --> 01:03:46.820
儿子，你确实让我去了那里
You really had me going there, son.

01:03:46.960 --> 01:03:50.650
那些年最糟糕的维京人
All those years of the worst Viking

01:03:50.790 --> 01:03:53.030
伯克郡人所见过的
Berk has ever seen.

01:03:53.170 --> 01:03:55.030
奥丁，这很艰难
Odin, it was rough.

01:03:55.170 --> 01:03:56.690
我几乎已经放弃你了
I almost gave up on you.

01:03:56.830 --> 01:03:59.830
而一直以来，你都对我有所隐瞒
And all the while, you were holding out on me.

01:04:01.140 --> 01:04:03.180
全能的雷神
Thor almighty.

01:04:03.320 --> 01:04:05.460
谁会想到龙训练
Who would have thought that dragon training

01:04:05.600 --> 01:04:08.560
本来就是你大放异彩的地方，是吧？
would have been your place to shine, huh?

01:04:08.700 --> 01:04:11.640
啊，你甚至可能赢得“顶级杀手”称号
Ah, you might even win Top Slayer.

01:04:11.770 --> 01:04:13.150
就像你老爸一样
Just like your old man.

01:04:13.290 --> 01:04:15.160
谁知道呢？
Who knows?

01:04:15.290 --> 01:04:16.780
你知道...
You know...

01:04:16.920 --> 01:04:18.880
你在拳击场上表现得如此出色……
With you doing so well in the ring...

01:04:19.020 --> 01:04:20.640
我要…我要…
I'm gonna... I'm gonna...

01:04:20.780 --> 01:04:22.060
—坐下 —好的
-Sit. -Okay.

01:04:22.200 --> 01:04:25.200
我们终于有话可谈了
We finally have something to talk about.

01:04:32.590 --> 01:04:34.380
所以，我……
So, I...

01:04:44.880 --> 01:04:47.290
哦！哦，我，呃……
Oh! Oh, I, uh...

01:04:47.430 --> 01:04:49.880
我给你带了一些东西……
I brought you something...

01:04:50.020 --> 01:04:52.370
为了……为了，呃……
To... to, uh...

01:04:52.500 --> 01:04:55.680
保证你在拳击场内的安全
keep you safe in the ring.

01:04:57.960 --> 01:05:00.890
你的母亲一定希望你拥有它
Your mother would have wanted you to have it.

01:05:01.720 --> 01:05:03.760
哇哦 呃，谢谢
W-Wow. Uh, thanks.

01:05:03.900 --> 01:05:05.660
这是她胸甲的一半
It's half of her breastplate.

01:05:07.070 --> 01:05:09.110
配套
Matching set.

01:05:09.250 --> 01:05:11.520
让她...
Keeps her...

01:05:11.660 --> 01:05:13.800
它让她靠近你，你知道吗？
It keeps her close, you know?

01:05:15.700 --> 01:05:17.320
儿子，自豪地穿上它
Wear it proudly, son.

01:05:17.460 --> 01:05:20.530
你已经履行了你的承诺
You've held up your end of the deal.

01:05:25.260 --> 01:05:26.680
是的
Yeah.

01:05:26.810 --> 01:05:29.060
-是啊 累了 -是啊，我要……
-Yeah. Tired. -Yeah, I'm gonna...

01:05:29.200 --> 01:05:31.090
—我要去睡觉了 —呃，聊得不错
-I'm gonna get some s-sleep. -Uh, good talk.

01:05:31.230 --> 01:05:32.820
—明天是个重要的日子 —是的
-Big day tomorrow. -Yeah.

01:05:32.960 --> 01:05:34.330
火焰试炼，它会消耗你很多的精力
The Trial of Flame, and it takes a lot out of you.

01:05:34.410 --> 01:05:36.050
是的，火焰试炼……火焰
Yeah, Trial of Flames... Flame.

01:05:36.130 --> 01:05:37.880
—祝你好运 —好的，谢谢你，谢谢你
-Good luck with that. -Yeah, thank you, thank you

01:05:37.960 --> 01:05:38.990
—呃……胸帽 —我希望你喜欢……
-for the, uh... the breast hat. -I hope you like the...

01:05:39.070 --> 01:05:41.620
—帽子 是的 —是的
-Hat. Yeah. -Yeah.

01:05:41.760 --> 01:05:44.730
好的，那么...晚安
Okay, well... good night.

01:05:53.630 --> 01:05:55.260
别再耍你的花招了
No more of your tricks.

01:05:55.390 --> 01:05:57.240
-我今天要参加“Top Slayer”考试 -是的，是的，好的
-I'm taking Top Slayer today. -Yeah, yeah, okay.

01:05:57.330 --> 01:05:59.950
这、这都是你的了 Top-Top 尽情杀戮吧
It's-it's all yours. Top-Top Slay away.

01:06:00.090 --> 01:06:01.300
对不起
Sorry.

01:06:23.320 --> 01:06:26.010
最后一次机会 好好把握
Last chance. Make it count.

01:06:32.290 --> 01:06:33.710
快点！
Come on!

01:06:33.850 --> 01:06:35.630
-加油，阿斯特丽德！你成功了！-加油，希卡普！
-Go on, Astrid! You got it! -Come on, Hiccup!

01:06:35.710 --> 01:06:38.200
—继续！—来吧！
-Go on! -Come on!

01:06:42.170 --> 01:06:43.410
不！
No!

01:06:43.550 --> 01:06:46.030
半巨魔的儿子，吃老鼠……
Son of a half-troll, rat-eating...

01:06:46.170 --> 01:06:47.900
很高兴看到她能优雅地处理这件事
Glad to see she's handling it gracefully.

01:06:48.030 --> 01:06:49.450
你！
You!

01:06:53.490 --> 01:06:55.730
嗯，好的
Uh, okay.

01:06:55.870 --> 01:06:57.300
—稍后 —嘿，嘿 别那么急
-Later. -Hey, hey. Not so fast.

01:06:57.390 --> 01:06:58.790
—安静点 —不，我不能
-Quiet down. -No, I can't.

01:06:58.910 --> 01:07:00.100
—我要迟到了，呃...—什么？
-I'm gonna be late for, uh... -What?

01:07:00.180 --> 01:07:01.600
到底因为什么事迟到？
Late for what, exactly?

01:07:01.740 --> 01:07:03.100
—再过一年……—闭嘴
-Another year... -Shut up.

01:07:03.190 --> 01:07:04.520
...以及另一场火焰试炼
...and another Trial of Flame

01:07:04.600 --> 01:07:06.090
已经结束了
has come to an end.

01:07:06.220 --> 01:07:09.680
戈蒂长老已经做出了决定
Elder Gothi has made her decision.

01:07:11.750 --> 01:07:16.540
新的 Top Slayer 将是...
The new Top Slayer will be...

01:07:38.080 --> 01:07:40.090
你成功了，希卡普
You've done it, Hiccup.

01:07:40.220 --> 01:07:41.880
你赢得了火焰试炼
You won the Trial of Flame.

01:07:42.020 --> 01:07:43.400
你要杀死那条龙
You get to kill the dragon.

01:07:43.540 --> 01:07:45.260
那是我的儿子！
That's my boy!

01:07:49.030 --> 01:07:52.200
希卡普，你赢了！
Hiccup, you won!

01:07:54.240 --> 01:07:56.690
哇！是啊
Whoa! Yeah.

01:07:56.830 --> 01:07:58.240
我太高兴了
Hooray me.

01:07:58.380 --> 01:07:59.970
我等不及了……
I can't wait to...

01:08:00.110 --> 01:08:02.310
打败它并且永不回来
Beat it and never come back.

01:08:02.450 --> 01:08:04.180
好了，伙计 时间到了
All right, bud. Time's up.

01:08:04.320 --> 01:08:06.110
我的想法完全一样
My thoughts exactly.

01:08:06.250 --> 01:08:08.150
你、你到底在干什么，呃……
Wh-What are you, uh...

01:08:08.290 --> 01:08:10.120
你在这里干什么？
What are you doing here?

01:08:10.250 --> 01:08:12.010
—寻找答案 —嗯？
-Looking for answers. -Huh?

01:08:12.150 --> 01:08:13.500
你在这里干什么？
What are you doing here?

01:08:13.640 --> 01:08:15.190
巴德是谁？你的教练？
Who's Bud? Your trainer?

01:08:15.330 --> 01:08:16.600
他给你穿这身衣服了吗？
Did he dress you up in this?

01:08:16.740 --> 01:08:18.430
呃，我知道这看起来很可疑，
Uh, I-I know this looks suspicious,

01:08:18.570 --> 01:08:20.750
但有趣的是，我，呃......
but f-funnily enough, I, uh...

01:08:20.880 --> 01:08:23.160
呃，你说得对！你说得对 我，呃……
Uh, you're right! You're right. I, uh...

01:08:23.300 --> 01:08:24.820
我不再说谎了
I'm through with the lies.

01:08:24.960 --> 01:08:27.240
我一直在做服装，所以，嗯，你明白我的意思了
I've been making outfits, so, um, you got me.

01:08:27.370 --> 01:08:28.310
是时候让每个人都知道了
It's time everybody knew.

01:08:28.440 --> 01:08:29.790
带我回去就好
Just take me back.

01:08:29.930 --> 01:08:31.410
哎哟！
Ow!

01:08:31.550 --> 01:08:32.620
你为什么要这么做？
Why would you do that?

01:08:32.760 --> 01:08:34.070
这都是谎言
That's for the lies.

01:08:35.520 --> 01:08:37.900
其他一切都如此
And that's for everything else.

01:08:39.490 --> 01:08:41.320
哦，不
Oh, no.

01:08:41.460 --> 01:08:43.360
快跑！快跑！
Run. Run!

01:08:43.490 --> 01:08:44.810
不不不
No! No.

01:08:44.940 --> 01:08:46.630
—什么... —无牙仔，不！
-What... -Toothless, no!

01:08:46.770 --> 01:08:47.950
停下来，没关系
Stop. It's okay.

01:08:48.080 --> 01:08:50.640
她是我的朋友，她是我的朋友
She's a friend. She's a friend.

01:08:54.950 --> 01:08:58.030
无牙仔，阿斯特丽德 阿斯特丽德，无牙仔
Toothless, Astrid. Astrid, Toothless.

01:08:58.160 --> 01:09:01.270
那个，呃......夜煞
The, uh... the Night Fury.

01:09:06.760 --> 01:09:08.790
我不会
I wouldn't.

01:09:13.180 --> 01:09:14.800
我们死了
We're dead.

01:09:16.700 --> 01:09:19.390
嘿 你想去哪儿？
Hey. Where do you think you're going?

01:09:50.250 --> 01:09:52.560
希卡普！放我下来！
Hiccup! Get me down from here!

01:09:52.700 --> 01:09:54.580
你得给我一个解释的机会
You have to give me a chance to explain.

01:09:54.700 --> 01:09:57.020
我不听你说什么
I'm not listening to anything you have to say.

01:09:57.150 --> 01:09:58.840
那我就不说话了
Then I won't speak.

01:09:58.980 --> 01:10:00.880
让我们向您展示一下
Just let us show you.

01:10:01.020 --> 01:10:03.090
请吧，阿斯特丽德
Please, Astrid.

01:10:14.550 --> 01:10:15.790
这是什么？
What is this?

01:10:15.930 --> 01:10:18.240
呃，这是我的设计
Uh, it's my design.

01:10:19.070 --> 01:10:21.210
是的 差不多就是副队长
Yeah. Pretty much the cocaptain.

01:10:23.420 --> 01:10:25.840
那么我们就把这件事了结吧
Then let's get this over with.

01:10:26.770 --> 01:10:27.910
你明白了
You got it.

01:10:28.050 --> 01:10:31.220
无牙仔，我们把她打倒吧
Toothless, let's take her down.

01:10:32.220 --> 01:10:33.910
轻轻地
Gently.

01:10:34.880 --> 01:10:36.540
没什么可害怕的
Nothing to be afraid of.

01:10:43.270 --> 01:10:44.820
噢，感觉真好！
Oh, nice touch!

01:10:48.450 --> 01:10:50.000
我以为你是他的副队长！
I thought you were his cocaptain!

01:10:50.140 --> 01:10:52.620
是的！这只是龙暂时故障！
I am! It's a temporary dragon malfunction!

01:10:56.320 --> 01:10:58.280
我们制定了整个系统，记得吗？
We worked out a whole system, remember?

01:11:00.180 --> 01:11:02.910
如果我们活下来，我就要杀了你！
If we survive, I'm gonna kill you!

01:11:07.090 --> 01:11:08.830
现在开始旋转
And now the spinning.

01:11:08.910 --> 01:11:12.300
谢谢你，你这个没用的爬虫
Thank you for nothing, you useless reptile.

01:11:12.440 --> 01:11:14.750
请让它停止
Please just make it stop.

01:11:16.580 --> 01:11:18.920
显然我不是掌控一切的人
I'm clearly not the one in control.

01:11:19.060 --> 01:11:20.340
那我就抱歉了！
Then I'm sorry!

01:11:20.480 --> 01:11:23.310
无牙仔，对不起！
Toothless, I'm sorry!

01:13:05.550 --> 01:13:07.030
美好的
Fine.

01:13:08.550 --> 01:13:10.420
你说得很清楚
You made your point.

01:13:12.620 --> 01:13:15.830
这并不能改变你明天必须杀死一个人的事实
It doesn't change the fact you have to kill one tomorrow.

01:13:17.530 --> 01:13:18.940
但如果我们能改变你的想法……
But if we can change your mind...

01:13:19.080 --> 01:13:20.600
什么？
What?

01:13:20.740 --> 01:13:22.700
你要带大家去进行一次神奇的旅程吗？
You gonna take everyone up for a magical ride?

01:13:25.600 --> 01:13:28.740
这并不能抹去他们对我们所做的一切，希卡普
It won't erase what they've done to us, Hiccup.

01:13:29.680 --> 01:13:31.400
它们捕猎我们，偷走我们的食物
They hunt us, steal our food.

01:13:31.540 --> 01:13:33.230
其中一个人带走了我妈妈
And one of them took my mom.

01:13:33.370 --> 01:13:34.960
但我们就只能继续互相残杀吗？
But do we just keep killing one another?

01:13:35.100 --> 01:13:37.060
相对于...？
As opposed to...?

01:13:37.200 --> 01:13:39.270
我不知道
I-I don't know.

01:13:40.580 --> 01:13:44.280
但是你搞砸了我们的逃跑计划，所以我需要一点时间
But you botched our escape plan, so I'm gonna need a minute.

01:13:48.000 --> 01:13:51.630
好吧，我可能不会告发你
Well, I might not snitch on you.

01:13:52.770 --> 01:13:55.010
我们也许不会把你扔进海里
And we might not drop you in the sea.

01:13:59.190 --> 01:14:01.850
巴德？怎么了？
Bud? What's up?

01:14:01.980 --> 01:14:03.300
它是什么？
What is it?

01:14:03.430 --> 01:14:06.090
嘿 嘿
Hey. Hey.

01:14:07.230 --> 01:14:08.130
下来！
Get down!

01:14:11.030 --> 01:14:13.860
无牙仔，带我们离开这里
Toothless, get us out of here.

01:14:18.900 --> 01:14:22.000
看起来他们正在拖运猎物
It looks like they're hauling in their kill.

01:14:22.140 --> 01:14:24.280
那我们又是什么呢？
Then what does that make us?

01:15:00.080 --> 01:15:02.420
龙巢
The dragons' nest.

01:15:03.490 --> 01:15:05.840
