然后发生了一些疯狂的事情
Then something crazy.

01:31:46.390 --> 01:31:48.500
这才像样
That's more like it.

01:31:54.190 --> 01:31:55.780
表明你的立场
Sound your positions.

01:31:55.920 --> 01:31:57.540
保持在听力范围内
Stay within earshot.

01:31:57.680 --> 01:31:59.990
到船尾有一长度
One length to your stern.

01:32:00.130 --> 01:32:02.370
在你的右舷
On your starboard flank.

01:32:02.510 --> 01:32:04.580
他们为什么不进攻？
Why aren't they attacking?

01:32:04.720 --> 01:32:06.960
也许他们知道一些我们不知道的事情
Maybe they know something we don't.

01:32:09.900 --> 01:32:11.730
你只是一个自讨苦吃的人吗？
Are you just a glutton for punishment or what?

01:32:11.870 --> 01:32:14.660
这次我们有机会奋起反抗
We have a fighting chance this time.

01:32:16.320 --> 01:32:18.560
感谢 Hiccup
Thanks to Hiccup.

01:32:18.700 --> 01:32:20.240
你认为我们还要多久...
How long do you think we're gonna...

01:32:20.320 --> 01:32:22.840
嘘
Shh.

01:32:32.200 --> 01:32:34.270
让开，德吕尔
Step aside, Drül.

01:32:49.460 --> 01:32:52.420
— 把桨放上去！— 把桨放进去
-Ship the oars! -Oars in.

01:33:05.610 --> 01:33:07.400
好的，等一下
Okay, wait.

01:33:07.540 --> 01:33:10.890
你简直是在全村人面前丢脸
You just disgraced yourself in front of the whole village.

01:33:11.030 --> 01:33:13.100
—我们为什么要听你的？—因为我这么说
-Why would we listen to you? -'Cause I said so.

01:33:13.240 --> 01:33:15.310
没错 大家注意听
Exactly. Pay attention, gang.

01:33:15.450 --> 01:33:18.000
听着，我爸爸的本意是好的，但他很固执
Look, my dad means well, but he's stubborn.

01:33:18.140 --> 01:33:20.000
他即将陷入困境，
And he's about to be way in over his head,

01:33:20.140 --> 01:33:21.140
所以这取决于我们
so it's up to us.

01:33:21.250 --> 01:33:22.660
我们？
Us?

01:33:22.800 --> 01:33:24.660
如果没有你们，我不可能完成这个任务
I can't pull this off without you guys.

01:33:24.800 --> 01:33:26.630
你们每个人都有自己独特的才华
And you all have something special to offer.

01:33:26.770 --> 01:33:28.530
别再说了
Say no more.

01:33:28.670 --> 01:33:31.980
你很明智地寻找了世界上最致命的武器
You were wise to seek the world's most deadly weapon.

01:33:32.120 --> 01:33:33.530
这就是我
It's me.

01:33:33.670 --> 01:33:35.070
你有狂野的一面，我喜欢这一点
You've got a wild side, and I like it.

01:33:35.160 --> 01:33:36.050
阿斯特丽德，你是我们最强大的战士
Astrid, you're our strongest fighter.

01:33:36.190 --> 01:33:37.190
我们需要你来领导我们
We need you to lead us.

01:33:37.300 --> 01:33:39.510
究竟带领我们去往何方？
Lead us where exactly?

01:33:39.640 --> 01:33:43.100
他们乘坐我们所有的船离开了
They left with every ship we have.

01:33:45.440 --> 01:33:47.030
跟着我
Stick with me.

01:33:51.280 --> 01:33:52.660
哦
Oh.

01:33:52.790 --> 01:33:55.140
事情就是这样发生的
That's where that went.

01:33:55.280 --> 01:33:57.970
保持低调 做好准备
Stay low. Be ready.

01:34:36.670 --> 01:34:38.560
我们到了
We're here.

01:34:56.000 --> 01:34:57.720
不，嗯嗯
No, uh-uh.

01:34:58.580 --> 01:35:01.040
希卡普，我……
Hiccup, I...

01:35:01.170 --> 01:35:03.240
放松
Relax.

01:35:06.040 --> 01:35:07.110
没关系
It's okay.

01:35:17.470 --> 01:35:19.570
呃，你要去哪儿？
Uh, where are you going?

01:35:19.710 --> 01:35:21.920
你需要一些东西来帮助你坚持下去
You're gonna need something to help you hold on.

01:35:22.060 --> 01:35:23.890
准备
Get ready.

01:35:24.020 --> 01:35:26.030
这将是一个漫长的夜晚
It's gonna be a long night.

01:35:32.830 --> 01:35:34.930
组成防线
Form a defensive line.

01:35:40.870 --> 01:35:43.250
磨快斧头，小伙子们！
Sharpen those axes, lads!

01:35:51.360 --> 01:35:53.190
首席
Chief.

01:35:53.330 --> 01:35:54.880
准备好了，酋长
Ready, Chief.

01:35:56.090 --> 01:35:59.680
—坚强起来 —是的，斯托伊克
-Stand strong. -Aye, Stoick.

01:35:59.820 --> 01:36:02.820
—让你的人民感到骄傲 —我们会的，斯托伊克
-Make your people proud. -We will, Stoick.

01:36:05.060 --> 01:36:07.100
今天我们摧毁
Today, we destroy

01:36:07.240 --> 01:36:11.420
一劳永逸地结束龙的统治
the reign of the dragon once and for all.

01:36:15.940 --> 01:36:19.840
不管怎样，它就在这里结束，就在此刻！
However this ends, it ends right here, right now!

01:36:21.630 --> 01:36:25.080
所以让我们把这些魔鬼送回地狱吧！
So let's send these devils back to hell!

01:37:43.060 --> 01:37:44.720
就这样吗？
Is that it?

01:37:44.850 --> 01:37:46.060
这个窝是我们的！
The nest is ours!

01:37:49.820 --> 01:37:52.100
这还没有结束
This isn't over.

01:38:00.110 --> 01:38:01.970
弄清楚！
Get clear!

01:38:02.110 --> 01:38:03.630
倒退！
Fall back!

01:38:03.770 --> 01:38:05.740
撤退！全体撤退！
Fall back! Everyone, fall back!

01:38:12.050 --> 01:38:13.230
撤退！
Retreat!

01:38:15.850 --> 01:38:17.230
移动！
Move!

01:38:45.290 --> 01:38:47.400
赶快上船！
Get to the ships!

01:38:47.540 --> 01:38:48.920
不！
No!

01:39:01.650 --> 01:39:03.450
到达岛的另一边
Get to the far side of the island.

01:39:03.590 --> 01:39:05.280
好的，酋长 我们出发吧！
Aye, Chief. Let's move!

01:39:05.420 --> 01:39:07.970
这边走！大家！
This way! All of you!

01:39:13.320 --> 01:39:15.430
—伙计们，离开这里！—跟我来！
-Get out of here, lads! -Follow me!

01:39:15.570 --> 01:39:17.260
戈伯，和其他人一起去
Gobber, go with the others.

01:39:17.390 --> 01:39:20.290
怎么了？你要去哪儿？
Why? Where are you going?

01:39:27.440 --> 01:39:28.960
事实上，我会留下来
Actually, I'm gonna stick around.

01:39:29.100 --> 01:39:31.200
你的眼神充满狂野
You've got that wild look in your eye.

01:39:32.310 --> 01:39:34.480
如果我把那东西给她们，她们就能得到一些时间
I can buy them some time if I give that thing

01:39:34.620 --> 01:39:35.650
猎取一些东西
something to hunt.

01:39:35.790 --> 01:39:37.350
我可以将这个时间加倍
And I can double that time.

01:39:38.900 --> 01:39:40.690
我知道 我是个心软的人
I know. I'm a big softy.

01:39:41.490 --> 01:39:44.460
你身上最柔软的部分是你的牙齿
Softest part of you is your teeth.

01:40:13.550 --> 01:40:17.010
记住，那是他们的女王
Remember, that thing is their queen.

01:40:17.140 --> 01:40:18.730
他们倾向于按照指示去做
They're inclined to do whatever it says.

01:40:18.870 --> 01:40:20.630
我们必须帮助他们反击
We've got to help them fight back.

01:40:23.630 --> 01:40:25.010
鱼腿，我们得到了什么？
Fishlegs, what do we got?

01:40:25.150 --> 01:40:27.980
哦，呃，重装甲的头骨和尾巴，
Ooh, uh, heavily armored skull and tail,

01:40:28.120 --> 01:40:30.330
非常适合打击和粉碎
perfect for bashing and crushing.

01:40:30.470 --> 01:40:32.710
眼睛小，鼻孔大
Small eyes, large nostrils.

01:40:32.850 --> 01:40:34.780
依靠听觉和嗅觉
Relies on hearing and smell.

01:40:34.920 --> 01:40:37.440
—知道了，阿斯特丽德 —好的
-Got it. Astrid. -Okay.

01:40:37.580 --> 01:40:40.510
鼻涕粗、鱼脚司，悬挂在它的盲点处
Snotlout, Fishlegs, hang in its blind spot.

01:40:40.650 --> 01:40:43.380
制造一些噪音，让它保持混乱
Make some noise. Keep it confused.

01:40:43.520 --> 01:40:46.000
拉夫，塔夫，找出它的射击极限
Ruff, Tuff, figure out its shot limit.

01:40:46.140 --> 01:40:47.280
让它疯狂
Make it mad.

01:40:47.420 --> 01:40:49.690
这是我们的特色！
That's our specialty!

01:40:51.140 --> 01:40:53.110
大家尽量不要被杀死！
Try not to get killed, guys!

01:41:03.160 --> 01:41:06.470
呃，这东西没有盲点
Uh, this thing doesn't have a blind spot.

01:41:10.060 --> 01:41:11.990
那里！
There!

01:41:16.480 --> 01:41:18.760
嘿，出价
Hey, bud.

01:41:18.900 --> 01:41:20.280
我很好
I'm good.

01:41:20.410 --> 01:41:21.790
当心
Be careful.

01:41:26.320 --> 01:41:28.870
我知道，我知道，但是我，呃......我现在在这里
I know, I know, but I'm, uh... I'm here now.

01:41:41.950 --> 01:41:43.510
继续敲击！
Keep hammering!

01:41:43.640 --> 01:41:46.510
但我们却混淆了自己的龙！
But we're confusing our own dragons!

01:41:46.650 --> 01:41:48.650
噢，不！
Oh, no!

01:41:54.790 --> 01:41:56.390
这边走！
This way!

01:41:56.520 --> 01:41:58.070
这边走！快点！快点！
This way! Come on! Come on!

01:41:58.210 --> 01:41:59.850
伙计们，继续前进！继续前进！加油！
Guys, keep moving! Keep moving! Come on!

01:41:59.940 --> 01:42:00.870
去！
Go!

01:42:01.010 --> 01:42:02.630
那是我的孩子吗？
Is that my kid?

01:42:02.770 --> 01:42:05.360
—鼻涕虫！—来吧！扔！
-Snotlout! -Come on! Throw it!

01:42:07.670 --> 01:42:09.700
哇哦，姑娘
Whoa, girl.

01:42:09.840 --> 01:42:11.500
正在下降
Going down.

01:42:14.090 --> 01:42:15.810
我没事
I'm okay.

01:42:15.950 --> 01:42:17.990
少一点就好
Less okay.

01:42:19.990 --> 01:42:22.300
我抓到你了，鱼脚司
I got you, Fishlegs.

01:42:31.110 --> 01:42:32.350
怎么了？
What's wrong?

01:42:32.490 --> 01:42:34.970
你的眼睛里进东西了吗？
Got something in your eye?

01:42:35.110 --> 01:42:38.420
是啊！这可是顶级杀手啊
Yeah! Now, that's a Top Slayer.

01:43:58.230 --> 01:43:59.920
你明白了，伙计
You got it, bud.

01:44:05.680 --> 01:44:07.240
呃呃
Hiccup.

01:44:09.550 --> 01:44:12.340
我只是想保护你
I was only trying to protect you.

01:44:12.480 --> 01:44:14.930
我知道，爸爸
I know, Dad.

01:44:15.070 --> 01:44:17.140
让我来回报你吧
Let me return the favor.

01:44:19.630 --> 01:44:21.700
无论那里发生什么，
Whatever happens up there,

01:44:21.840 --> 01:44:25.740
我很自豪地称你为我的儿子
I'm proud to call you my son.

01:44:29.710 --> 01:44:31.290
这就是我所需要的
And that's all I need.

01:44:32.780 --> 01:44:34.090
我们走吧
Let's go.

01:44:38.300 --> 01:44:39.610
他醒了！
He's up!

01:44:40.890 --> 01:44:42.650
你们两个，去抓 Snotlout
You two, get Snotlout.

01:44:42.790 --> 01:44:44.240
我会分散女王的注意力
I'll distract the queen.

01:44:46.280 --> 01:44:49.420
没错 看着我
That's right. Eyes on me.

01:44:51.630 --> 01:44:52.970
鼻涕虫！
Snotlout!

01:44:56.490 --> 01:44:57.560
现在！
Now!

01:44:57.700 --> 01:45:00.150
噢，你一定是在跟我开玩笑
Oh, you have got to be kidding me.

01:45:06.740 --> 01:45:08.370
哇哦！
Whoa!

01:45:13.300 --> 01:45:14.890
我简直不敢相信这真的有效
I can't believe that worked.

01:45:15.030 --> 01:45:17.240
是的
Yeah.

01:45:18.890 --> 01:45:21.660
不，不，不，姑娘
No, no, no, girl.

01:45:21.790 --> 01:45:24.310
反抗！别听她的！
Fight it! Don't listen to her!

01:45:24.450 --> 01:45:25.900
甩掉它！
Shake it off!

01:45:50.480 --> 01:45:52.380
阿斯特丽德
Astrid.

01:46:07.320 --> 01:46:09.250
你抓到她了吗？
Did you get her?

01:46:22.850 --> 01:46:24.230
去
Go.

01:46:27.240 --> 01:46:28.930
那东西有翅膀
That thing has wings.

01:46:29.070 --> 01:46:31.000
让我们看看它是否可以使用它们
Let's see if it can use them.

01:46:46.190 --> 01:46:48.120
您认为这样就行了吗？
You think that did it?

01:46:50.360 --> 01:46:51.570
是的
Yep.

01:47:06.760 --> 01:47:09.660
好了，伙计，该消失了
All right, bud. It's time to disappear.

01:47:14.980 --> 01:47:17.460
来了！
Here it comes!

01:47:22.980 --> 01:47:25.780
你真是一个出色的领袖
Quite the chief you have in the making there.

01:47:25.920 --> 01:47:27.160
机会
Aye.

01:48:08.170 --> 01:48:09.820
小心！
Watch out!

01:48:13.550 --> 01:48:15.040
好的，时间到了
Okay, time's up.

01:48:15.170 --> 01:48:17.070
让我们看看这是否有效
Let's see if this works.

01:48:22.210 --> 01:48:23.770
这就是你所拥有的一切吗？
Is that all you've got?

01:48:42.960 --> 01:48:44.480
跟我在一起吧，伙计！
Stay with me, bud!

01:48:44.620 --> 01:48:46.480
再等一会儿！
Just a little bit longer!

01:48:47.550 --> 01:48:49.310
坚持住，无牙仔！
Hold, Toothless!

01:48:51.830 --> 01:48:53.520
现在！
Now!

01:49:15.230 --> 01:49:17.440
是的，伙计，我们......不！
Yeah, bud, we... No!

01:49:36.600 --> 01:49:38.770
呃呃！
Hiccup!

01:49:43.050 --> 01:49:45.090
呃呃？
Hiccup?

01:49:45.230 --> 01:49:46.710
儿子？
Son?

01:49:48.540 --> 01:49:50.540
呃呃！
Hiccup!

01:50:05.460 --> 01:50:07.250
噢，他的
Oh, son.

01:50:19.470 --> 01:50:21.470
我很抱歉
I'm so sorry.

01:51:33.410 --> 01:51:35.170
呃呃
Hiccup.

01:51:43.210 --> 01:51:45.350
他还活着 他还活着！
He's alive. He's alive!

01:51:48.520 --> 01:51:50.040
是的！
Yeah!

01:51:50.180 --> 01:51:52.220
是的！
Yes!

01:52:03.020 --> 01:52:05.160
谢谢...
Thank you...

01:52:06.060 --> 01:52:08.230
...为了救我的儿子
...for saving my son.

01:52:09.580 --> 01:52:12.580
嗯，你知道……他的大部分情况
Well, you know... most of him.

01:52:28.460 --> 01:52:30.080
嘿，无牙仔
Hey, Toothless.

01:52:32.090 --> 01:52:33.330
好的
Okay.

01:52:38.820 --> 01:52:40.650
我在我的家里
I'm in my house.

01:52:42.160 --> 01:52:43.790
你，你在我家
You-You're in my house.

01:52:43.920 --> 01:52:46.480
我爸爸知道你在这里吗？
D-Does my dad know you're here?

01:52:46.620 --> 01:52:49.100
哦，来吧
Oh, come on.

01:53:37.010 --> 01:53:38.630
谢谢，伙计
Thanks, bud.

01:53:42.190 --> 01:53:44.190
好的，我们开始吧
Okay, here we go.

01:54:13.700 --> 01:54:15.330
无牙仔，留下来
Toothless, stay.

01:54:19.050 --> 01:54:21.780
嘿，嘿，嘿！你不是应该去睡觉吗？
Hey, hey, hey! Shouldn't you be in bed?

01:54:23.510 --> 01:54:25.680
好的 大家抓紧了
Okay. Hold on tight, guys.

01:54:25.820 --> 01:54:28.130
开始了
Here we go.

01:54:28.270 --> 01:54:29.960
哇哦，哇哦！
Whoa, whoa!

01:54:36.730 --> 01:54:38.310
嘿！嘿！
Hey! Hey!

01:54:38.450 --> 01:54:40.870
就这样！
There you go!

01:54:45.220 --> 01:54:48.530
—他在那儿！哦，哦 —哦！好的
-There he is! Oh, oh. -Oh! Okay.

01:54:49.390 --> 01:54:51.640
那么，您觉得怎么样？
So, what do you think?

01:54:51.780 --> 01:54:54.090
自从你离开后，发生了一些变化
A few changes since you've been out.

01:54:54.230 --> 01:54:57.850
我告诉你，飞回这里真是一次相当不错的经历
Flying back here was, uh, quite an experience, let me tell you.

01:54:57.990 --> 01:55:00.610
等等，等等，你……你骑着龙？
Wait, wait, you... you rode a dragon?

01:55:00.750 --> 01:55:02.100
嗯...嗯，那只怪物被烧死了
Well... well, that monster burned

01:55:02.240 --> 01:55:03.750
我们所有的船，所以我们并没有
all of our ships, so we didn't really

01:55:03.890 --> 01:55:05.290
— 有很多... — 打嗝！
-have much of a... -Hiccup!

01:55:05.380 --> 01:55:06.690
哦，不
Oh, no.

01:55:06.830 --> 01:55:08.690
这次我做了什么？
What'd I do this time?

01:55:08.830 --> 01:55:09.760
哎哟！
Ow!

01:55:09.900 --> 01:55:11.450
那是为了吓唬我
That's for scaring me.

01:55:11.590 --> 01:55:13.900
好吧，会一直这样吗？因为……
Okay, is it always gonna be like this? 'Cause...

01:55:16.700 --> 01:55:19.250
其他一切都如此
And that's for everything else.

01:55:19.390 --> 01:55:22.150
你知道，因为......因为我......我可以习惯这一点
You know, 'cause... 'cause I... I-I could get used to that.

01:55:22.290 --> 01:55:23.880
是的
Yep.

01:55:24.020 --> 01:55:28.990
事实证明，我们所需要的只是多一点这样的事
Turns out all we needed was a little more of this.

01:55:29.750 --> 01:55:31.610
你刚才向我所有人做了手势
You just gestured to all of me.

01:55:31.750 --> 01:55:34.720
嗯，你们大多数人都知道
Well, you know, most of you.

01:55:34.850 --> 01:55:37.030
新的腿是我亲手做的，只需轻轻一划
New leg is my handiwork with just a dash

01:55:37.170 --> 01:55:39.650
充分展现你的古怪天赋
of your kooky flair thrown in for good measure.

01:55:39.790 --> 01:55:40.830
开始了
Here we go.

01:55:40.960 --> 01:55:42.340
欢迎回家
Welcome home.

01:55:42.480 --> 01:55:43.760
—你重建了它？—是的
-You rebuilt it? -Yeah.

01:55:43.900 --> 01:55:45.660
